Author: thecalcographer
Text: Sometimes if you google it, the internet has relatively accurate calorie estimates for disneyland food.  It always makes me feel much better to at least get an idea.

Author: 3cats_in_atrenchcoat
Text: You walked a ton I’m sure! One day doesn’t mean anything, you take care of yourself. It’s important to treat yourself to fun times and cut loose from time to time. If it’s sticking around in your head focus on keeping up healthy habits in the next few weeks.
